trans-unit.source: Represents the method that will handle the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartsConnected"></xref> and <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartsDisconnected"></xref> events of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager"></xref> control.
trans-unit.target: 처리 하는 메서드를 나타냅니다는 <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartsConnected"> </xref> 및 <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartsDisconnected"> </xref> 의 이벤트는 <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager"> </xref> 제어 합니다.

trans-unit.source: The WebPartConnectionsEventHandler class defines a handler delegate for two events that occur on the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager> control: the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartsConnected> event and the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartsDisconnected> event.
trans-unit.target: WebPartConnectionsEventHandler 클래스 정의에서 발생 하는 두 개의 이벤트 처리기 대리자는 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>제어:는 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartsConnected>이벤트 및 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartsDisconnected>이벤트.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartsDisconnected> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartsConnected> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>

trans-unit.source: The method that handles the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartsConnected> event is the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.OnWebPartsConnected%2A> method.

The method that handles the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartsDisconnected> event is the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.OnWebPartsDisconnected%2A> method.
In both cases, the event data are contained in a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartConnectionsEventArgs> object.
trans-unit.target: 두 경우 모두, 이벤트 데이터에 포함 되어는 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartConnectionsEventArgs>개체입니다.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartConnectionsEventArgs>
